{"tid":1563673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中秋獅子山 翌日天水圍 星期日銅鑼灣] 我正式宣佈 #黃店challenge 正式上綫！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-12T13:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:11:47.000Z","uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7bf3646d1764bbe46b8adedff428fa8d4867bda","tid":1563673,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"最近發現黃絲暴徒開嘅店舖越嚟越多人幫襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗鼓勵大家用港幣懲罰呢啲舖頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我宣佈推出 #黃店challenge！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n每幫襯一間黃絲店舖嗰陣影一張相<br />\n然後放上 ig story/facebook 再 tag 埋 #黃店challenge<br />\n咁大家就可以知道邊啲舖頭老細係黃絲暴徒<br />\n然後一齊去經濟制裁佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又或者大家幫襯其他舖頭時 遇到一啲黃絲暴徒員工/老細<br />\n都可以用呢個 tag 去報料<br />\n等佢哋知道撐暴徒係會有經濟後果 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家最好可以 tag 埋親戚朋友陪你一齊玩啦<br />\n比人 tag 完記得要去幫襯一間黃店 用經濟懲罰佢哋喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422c8acaa0117af12545fbc7904474a0e43e89bc","tid":1563673,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都唔知有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔對得住烈士同被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期五 <span style=\"color: red;\">獅子山之路</span> 7:30 樂富 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KQxrNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KQxrNJ.png&h=c869dffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期六 <span style=\"color: red;\">天水圍親子遊行</span> 2:30 天秀公園</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0LtKzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0LtKzJ.jpg&h=85f2aac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期日 <span style=\"color: red;\">金鐘民陣遊行</span> 2:30 東角道</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/12/185803_2cefd2fa1345b60607d92f6a90928d20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F185803_2cefd2fa1345b60607d92f6a90928d20.png&h=a89435a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手做文宣同連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543b571ba83c43989cd6453fe24a57626b12986f","tid":1563673,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:15:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /><